This application incorporates or is inspired by the following open-source projects:

1. python-kasa (https://github.com/python-kasa/python-kasa)
   Copyright (C) python-kasa contributors
   Licensed under GNU General Public License v3.0
   
   This project uses python-kasa library for communication with TP-Link Kasa
   smart devices. The python-kasa library provides the core functionality for
   device discovery, control, and data retrieval.

2. PeaNUT (https://github.com/brandawg93/peanut)
   Copyright (C) Brandon Garcia and PeaNUT contributors
   Licensed under Apache License 2.0
   
   The user interface design and monitoring dashboard concepts were inspired by
   PeaNUT's approach to displaying UPS monitoring data. While no code was
   directly copied, the visual layout and information presentation patterns
   influenced the design of this application.

